<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Bobo Analytics</title>

  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#020617,#3b0764);
      color:white;
    }

    header{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      padding:15px 25px;
      background:#020617;
      border-bottom:1px solid #06b6d4;
    }

    .logo{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
      font-weight:bold;
      font-size:20px;
    }

    .hero{
      text-align:center;
      padding:120px 20px 60px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      font-size:48px;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    .hero p{
      font-size:20px;
      opacity:0.8;
    }

    .card{
      max-width:800px;
      margin:60px auto;
      background:#020617;
      padding:40px;
      border-radius:16px;
      text-align:center;
      box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    footer{
      background:#020617;
      color:white;
      text-align:center;
      padding:40px 20px;
      margin-top:80px;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    footer a{
      color:#22d3ee;
      text-decoration:none;
      margin:0 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <img src="/logo.png" width="40"/>
    Bobo Analytics
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>AI Analytics Platform</h1>
  <p>Turn business data into intelligent decisions.</p>
</section>

<div class="card">
  <h2>Welcome to Bobo Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    Smart analytics solutions designed for every industry.
    Upload data, analyze insights, and grow your business using AI-powered intelligence.
  </p>
</div>


<footer>

  <h3>Bobo Analytics</h3>

  <p style="max-width:700px;margin:auto;opacity:0.8;font-size:14px;">
    Smart analytics solutions designed for modern businesses.
    Transform data into intelligent decisions using AI-powered insights.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top:20px;font-size:14px;">
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms & Conditions</a>
    <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-top:25px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6;">
    © 2026 Bobo Analytics — Smart Analytics for Smarter Business
  </p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>